Rena Riffel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rena_Riffel 0 Rena Riffel (born March 5, 1969) is an American actress, singer, dancer, model, writer, producer, and director. She is known for her supporting roles in films such as Showgirls, Striptease, and Mulholland Drive.
